enum Navico::Protocol::NRP::eTargetState

Enumerations for Target-Tracking target states.

Enumerator
eAcquiringTarget 

Attempting to acquire target.

eSafeTarget 

Target acquired and not on a collision course.

eDangerousTarget 

Target acquired and may be on a collision course.

eLostTarget 

Target has been lost and needs to be cancelled an reacquired.

eAcquireFailure 

Failed to acquire a target.

eOutOfRange 

Target is now out of range.

eLostOutOfRange 

Target lost due to staying out of range.

eFailAcquireMax 

Acquire failed because no target IDs were free.

eFailAcquirePos 

Acquire failed because the position was invalid.

eBadState
